data.description: This charming custom built Marquee home in The Settlement at Powhatan Creek host an open concept floor plan, offering high ceilings w/natural light, Greatroom w/gas fireplace, a delightful sunroom overlooking the wooded area in the rear of the home. Spacious kitchen w/ample cabinets, granite countertops, ss appliances, walk-in pantry & breakfast bar. Lovely formal dining room w/tray ceiling, crown, chair, & picture molding. Primary Suite w/huge walk-in closet plus a guest BR & BA on the first floor. Upstairs you will find 2 BR & a full BA plus lots of storage. SQ FT does not reflect tax records. Per 2022 appraisal sqft is 2695.  Don't miss out on this great home in a quaint 55+community w/fantastic amenities!
